OL,3,CDomestic abuse charities warn
OL,4,Csurvivors ahead of Sunday's emergency
OL,5,Calert test
OL,7,FDomestic abuse charities have warned
OL,8,Fan emergency alert test taking place
OL,9,Fon Sunday 7th September could put
OL,10,Fsurvivors at risk.
OL,12,FThe alert will blast a sound for 10
OL,13,Fseconds, at 3pm, to all 4G and 5G
OL,14,Fphones in the UK.
OL,16,FThe alert could reveal the existence
OL,17,Fof a survivor's hidden second phone
OL,18,Fused to seek help, putting them at
OL,19,Fimmediate danger, the charities have
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
