OL,4,Csurvivors ahead of Sunday's emergency
OL,5,Calert test
OL,7,FThose at risk are being urged to turn
OL,8,Fthe emergency alert off in their phone
OL,9,Fsettings.
OL,11,FThe alert will still sound if phones
OL,12,Fare on silent, and there is also the
OL,13,Fdanger that phones that have been
OL,14,Fswitched off could still sound when
OL,15,Fturned back on after the alert.
OL,17,FRefuge is a Domestic abuse charity
OL,18,Fhighlighting the risk the alert poses
OL,19,Fto survivors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
