OL,4,Csurvivors ahead of Sunday's emergency
OL,5,Calert test
OL,7,FEllie Butt, Refuge's Head of Policy
OL,8,Fand Public Affairs said: "There will
OL,9,Fbe a significant number of people
OL,10,Fwhere this could be really dangerous
OL,11,Ffor them, if their perpetrator finds
OL,12,Fout that they have a secondary phone,
OL,13,Fthat they are trying to pull back some
OL,14,Fof that control, and perhaps planning
OL,15,Fto leave"
OL,17,FThis is the second test of the system
OL,18,Fdesigned to warn the public in the
OL,19,Fevent of life-threatening emergencies,
OL,20,Fsuch as floods or wildfires.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
