OL,5,Calert test
OL,7,FCharities say information on how to
OL,8,Fswitch the alert off is buried deep in
OL,9,Fthe government website, making it
OL,10,Fdifficult to find.
OL,12,FThey say the government needs to do
OL,13,Fmore to help survivors of domestic
OL,14,Fabuse, especially when it comes to
OL,15,Fpolicymaking: "We really need to be
OL,16,Fthinking about people that are
OL,17,Fexperiencing domestic abuse in all
OL,18,Fpublic policy. Sadly, 1 in 4 women are
OL,19,Fsubject to domestic abuse over their
OL,20,Flifetime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
