OL,4,Csurvivors ahead of Sunday's emergency
OL,5,Calert test
OL,7,FRefuge says that while each test
OL,8,Fpresents risk to survivors, it also
OL,9,Fgives opportunity to turn the function
OL,10,Foff now, so that if there were a real
OL,11,Femergency, they would not be caught
OL,12,Foff guard.
OL,14,F"It's a good illustration of how we
OL,15,Fcan be doing something, thinking about
OL,16,Fflood defences and informing people
OL,17,Fabout danger. But at the same time, we
OL,18,Fneed to be thinking about the women
OL,19,Fthat are juggling risk and trying to
OL,20,Fkeep themselves safe and protect
OL,21,Fthemselves in their everyday lives."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
